            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="../../review/9745638/default.htm">香港的“人到中年”</a></h2>

                <div id="review_9745638_short" class="review-short" data-rid="9745638">
                    <div class="short-content">
                            <p class="spoiler-tip">这篇影评可能有剧透</p>

                        近来的港产片，不断涌入各种负能量，多数是充满悲观色彩和人文关怀的社会问题片。《逆流大叔》则以轻松幽默的笔触道出港人面对“逆流”迎难而上的乐观心态，剧情和笑点流畅自然，粤语对白一滴入魂，不见半点儿合拍片的味道。 这是编剧、作家陈咏燊首执导筒的处女作长片，故事讲...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-9745638-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_9745638_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_9745638_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="9745638" title="有用">
                        <img src="../../../https@img3.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-9745638">
                                31
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn down" data-rid="9745638" title="没用">
